dengan tugas darimu sekarang.

477
00:32:23,070 --> 00:32:25,590
Hatiku dan Yunxiu
saling terhubung.

478
00:32:25,710 --> 00:32:26,870
Tentu saja dia senang.

479
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:29,680
Maksudku, dibandingkan
diam saja di sini.

480
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,680
Dia lebih suka mencari Fengyang.

481
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:35,350
Jangan asal bicara di sini.

482
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:39,110
Jing Xin.

483
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:42,870
Kau sedang apa?

484
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,350
Membandingkan ukuran.

485
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:13,270
Aku takut kau dan Tuan Agung
mati tersedak.

486
00:33:15,820 --> 00:33:17,660
Raja cuka menumpahkan cuka.
[*ada yang cemburu]

487
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:19,720
Rasanya benar-benar sangat asam!

488
00:33:22,190 --> 00:33:22,830
Kau!

489
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:08,160
Aku baru membuatnya, cicipilah.

490
00:34:11,350 --> 00:34:12,590
Tuan Agung mahir memasak.

491
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:13,840
Namun, sekarang aku tak lapar.

492
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,350
Apa Jenderal perlu begitu waspada?

493
00:34:29,740 --> 00:34:31,220
Hanya tak mau
merepotkan Tuan Agung.

494
00:34:31,240 --> 00:34:32,070
Tak ada maksud lain.

495
00:34:36,990 --> 00:34:38,000
Kuambil dengan kain.

496
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:01,720
Apa dia memberitahuku
kue ini tak beracun?

497
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:04,790
Terlihat baik dari luar.

498
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:06,390
Pasti punya maksud tersembunyi.

499
00:35:29,160 --> 00:35:29,960
Dia datang.

500
00:35:35,160 --> 00:35:35,830
Ayo.

501
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,870
