Mo Fengyang latihan pedang, 'kan?

538
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:37,520
Tidak.

539
00:40:03,160 --> 00:40:04,740
Bukankah Yunxiu
yang tidur denganmu?

540
00:40:04,860 --> 00:40:06,100
